Package edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.configurationSpecification

This package specifies the bitstream details of the architectures supported and contains classes to automatically generate new part libraries.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
XilinxConfigurationSpecification Specifies the parameters for the configuration data associated with a Xilinx FPGA.
